OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy rain at first. Otherwise
OL,6,Fdry and rather cloudy, some hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine developing in the east during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Further rain spreading
OL,9,Feast later. Breezy in the north.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with light
OL,12,Fand patchy rain, the rain turning
OL,13,Fshowery through the night and
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy in the west.
OL,15,FStrengthening southwesterly winds with
OL,16,Frisk of coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
