OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRain spreading southeast in
OL,6,Fthe morning, heavy initially in the
OL,7,Fwest but lighter in the east. Then
OL,8,Fturning drier and brighter with a few
OL,9,Flight scattered showers. Strong winds
OL,10,Feasing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,For sunny spells on Sunday with the odd
OL,14,Fshower, but many places dry. Fairly
OL,15,Funsettled and changeable Monday and
OL,16,FTuesday with the risk of rain or
OL,17,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
